            "level": 2
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "items": [
              { "text": "Loss of function and pain are key features. Assess severity of disability." },
              { "text": "Distinguish between Joint Pain (Arthritis) and Bone Pain (Leukaemia, Myeloma, Metastases)." },
              { "text": "Identify the pattern: Onset, Progression, Symmetry, Number of joints." },
              { "text": "Decide if Inflammatory (Morning stiffness, warmth, swelling) or Mechanical (Pain on activity)." },
              { "text": "Look for extra-articular manifestations (Skin, Eyes, Lungs) which suggest systemic disease." }
            ]
          }
        ]
